---
title: Cheese Tortellini, Crispy Bacon and Creamy Pesto Sauce with Peppers and Spinach
description: Featuring creamy basil pesto sauce, bacon, sweet peppers and Parmesan, this dish combines fresh, summer flavours with the wintery comforts of hearty pasta for the best of all seasons.
